stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Draft : Case created by trigger<br/>(scheduler / risk event /<br/>admin manual / login detection)

  Draft --> InProgress : Customer authenticates<br/>and starts CRU flow
  Draft --> Expired : Customer does not start<br/>within 30 days

  InProgress --> Submitted : Customer clicks Submit<br/>with all required data
  InProgress --> Abandoned : No activity for 24h<br/>(retains partial progress,<br/>resumable via FR-030)

  Submitted --> UnderMakerReview : Appian claims case<br/>(AC-S09-02)
  UnderMakerReview --> PendingChecker : Maker forwards<br/>(AC-S09-03)
  UnderMakerReview --> RejectedByMaker : Maker rejects<br/>with reason

  PendingChecker --> Approved : Checker approves<br/>(AC-S09-05)
  PendingChecker --> Rejected : Checker rejects<br/>with reason
  PendingChecker --> UnderMakerReview : Checker returns<br/>(cycle ≤ 3)

  Rejected --> InProgress : Customer re-submits<br/>(cycle ≤ 3)
  RejectedByMaker --> InProgress : Customer re-submits<br/>(cycle ≤ 3)

  Rejected --> Escalated : Cycle 4 reached<br/>(AC-S09-07)
  RejectedByMaker --> Escalated : Cycle 4 reached
  Escalated --> Approved : Manager approves
  Escalated --> Closed : Manager closes<br/>(account remains Restricted)

  Approved --> [*] : DataHub sync fired;<br/>notifications sent;<br/>account status derives<br/>from Thought Machine
  Abandoned --> [*] : Closed by sweeper after N days
  Expired --> [*] : Closed
  Closed --> [*]
